{"tid":2433646,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［學校選班長］杯葛係最佳方式，你投白票即認同制度內可以改變。","createTime":"2021-03-05T04:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T06:29:01.000Z","uid":272819,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2fdc6becf526f59734fb93ba596e6bba6506b9","tid":2433646,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"是甘的，選班長。<br />\n學校整左個框框（要好乖乖聽話，邊個講學校壞話、唔好既地方就唔做得）<br />\n咁就有人出黎參加班長（樣衰、鹽濕、成日摸人大俾、淨係識刷鞋shine xxxxx&rsquo;s shoes」，重點係<span class=\"xx-large\">壞過凱婷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>）<br />\n咁有人就會話「選完班長話唔定可以改善好多學校政策Wor」<br />\n亦都有人話「小！選完都係佢做班長啦，投白票囉」<br />\n實際上，<span class=\"xx-large\">你投果下即認同佢設既玩法係OK，即變相支援學校既政策</span><br />\n即：全校每班（36人）得一張票當選+35人不投票<br />\n定係：一票支持+35人投白票=36人投票<br />\n咁我係學校都話依個方式都有人支持咁我點解要改變？<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">個班長咁樣衰，我外貌協會梗係唔投啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就係唔盡公民責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹咩</span></span>"},{"pid":"269fbc273b989ee73aae6a3e10afc18a7122c6be","tid":2433646,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6d22e868232c2e5e34726bd9902aa64349be56","tid":2433646,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8611d9220f4fb1d493c5524dcb7954e9c7572059","tid":2433646,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d726a42ba93f8701ab4d1c672f579448ec9315f","tid":2433646,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51362615